Mount Clinton is an unincorporated community located in Rockingham County, in the U.S. state of Virginia. It is located northeast of Clover Hill.[1]There are several Mennonite churches in the vicinity, one of which is located along the access road to the west.[2] This populated place also has portions in an adjacent county or counties
